milestones.description: Viswanath has become the top scorer for IND in ODIs with 394 runs, going past Gavaskar's 387
Kapil Dev has become the top wicket-taker for IND in ODIs with 14 wickets, going past Amarnath's 13
This is the highest match aggregate (457) involving teams Australia & India in ODIs
Kim Hughes and Allan Border's 80-run partnership is AUS's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 74 between Ian Chappell and Greg Chappell
